# Foundry Module Development

Canonical references:

- [Introduction to Module Development](https://foundryvtt.com/article/module-development/) тАФ official manifest, structure, and loading
- [Modules (Community Wiki)](https://foundryvtt.wiki/en/basics/Modules) тАФ module basics, installation, and development overview

## Module Layout

- `module.json` at the module root (required)
- Recommended folders: `scripts/`, `styles/`, `templates/`, `packs/`, `lang/`
- Module `id` must match the folder name (lowercase, hyphens only)

## Manifest Essentials

Required fields: `id`, `title`, `description`, `version`

- Prefer `esmodules` over legacy `scripts`
- Target Foundry **14.360** in `compatibility`
- Common optional fields: `languages`, `styles`, `packs`, `packFolders`, `relationships`, `socket`, `library`, `manifest`, `download`

## Entry Pattern

```javascript
Hooks.on("init", () => {
  // Register settings, libWrapper, CONFIG extensions
});

Hooks.on("ready", () => {
  // Game data is available
});
```

Modules only affect the game view тАФ not Setup or Join screens.

